urls.title: Cuomo says it's 'shocking' most new coronavirus hospitalizations are people who had been staying home
urls.description: Early look at data from 100 New York hospitals shows that 66% of new admissions related to the virus are people who were at home, Cuomo said.

text: Two-thirds of new COVID cases in NYC are from people who had been staying home, and not venturing out AT ALL. It's almost like maybe there was room for a non-cartoonish response after all https://t.co/vuchg9JnJF
